description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for a number of (bank) housekeepers to join our Housekeeping team, to cover annual leave, sickness and other absences on a casual basis. The rate of pay will be £8.72 per hour.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Applicants must ensure that the highest possible standards of cleanliness, hygiene and presentation are maintained at all times throughout the hospice and have the following attributes&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous housekeeping/cleaning experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relevant H&amp;S and COSHH knowledge&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Caring approach and ability to work with patients in a palliative care setting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to work on their own and as part of a team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The working patterns are variable over 7 days as below &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;7.00am – 10.30am/11.00am (weekdays)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; 8.00am – 1.00pm (7 days a week)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; 3.00pm – 7.00pm (weekends)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;3.30pm – 7.00pm (weekdays)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details please attachements or contact Ruth Garrett via email ruth.garrett@aintree.nhs.uk or on 0151 529 8389.&lt;/p&gt;
